   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ama Ghar Displaced Children Fund</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Many children were orphaned or displaced by disastrous 2015 earthquakes in Nepal. Ama Foundation worked with anti-trafficking organizations and the Nepal government to help find these children a safe home. Since 2015, we have taken 30 new children into our home, which can house 75 children - but we currently only have funding for the 46 children who currently live there. Your contribution helps us to take in more children and give them a loving home, an education and a future.</narrative>
  </description>
